last_episode_to_air.name: Boys
last_episode_to_air.overview: When Graft finally makes good on her threat to close down Metro Sexual, Langdon decides to put on a musical to save the clinic with his new theatre actor boyfriend Tim, but Steph is dubious of Tim and suspects his motives might not be entirely pure.

name: Metro Sexual
overview: Sexual health clinicians Stephanie and Langdon have a tough enough job as it is - battling odorous STIs, onerous patients and arduous colleagues - but when government cuts threaten to close them down they must do whatever it takes to save their clinic from the chopping block.
